<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Password Changed Successfully</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f9f9f9; color: #222; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #eee; padding: 32px; }
    h1 { color: #2b7cff; }
    .security-icon { max-width: 80px; width: 100%; height: auto; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .alert-box { background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; border-radius: 4px; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .alert-box p { margin: 0; color: #856404; }
    .footer { margin-top: 32px; font-size: 12px; color: #888; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #2b7cff; color: #fff; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 16px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <img src="{{SecurityIconUrl}}" alt="Security" class="security-icon" />
    </div>
    <h1>Password Changed Successfully</h1>
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    <p>This is a confirmation that your password has been changed successfully.</p>
    
    <div class="alert-box">
      <p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> If you did not make this change, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>Your account security is important to us. Here are some security tips:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Never share your password with anyone</li>
      <li>Use a strong, unique password</li>
      <li>Change your password regularly</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns, don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>
    Sprint Tracker Support Team</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      This is an automatic email, please do not reply.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
